fel.cvut.af.model.input

Class SelectOneEndpointOptionsInput

  • java.lang.Object
    • fel.cvut.af.model.input.Input
      • fel.cvut.af.model.input.EndpointOptionsInput
        • fel.cvut.af.model.input.SelectOneEndpointOptionsInput

  • @Entity
public class SelectOneEndpointOptionsInput
extends EndpointOptionsInput
    An entity class for Selectbox where only one value can be selected.

    The options can represent different value types, see Option and his descendants. The options are provided as a url leading to REST endpoint where options can be requested from.

    Use this class when Options has bigger size or you want to have those in different request. There is also an implementation of SelectOne where Options can be supplied directly as a persisted list. See SelectOneBasicOptionsInput.
